These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, hiking, baking, cooking, rock-climbing, photography, fishing
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher, bolivar, bongani, dunhill, cain, vegafina
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is in the middle##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | cooking | hiking | baking | singing | photography | fishing |
| Cigar   | havana    | dunhill   | bongani      | cain | bolivar    | swisher    | vegafina         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
House: ranch-style, wooden, tower, futuristic, gothic-revival, townhouse, cape-cod
There are 7 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite, milk, juice, lemonade
 1. the person drinking milk is the futuristic house##1
 2. the townhouse house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 4. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the townhouse house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 7. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking milk is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the tower house##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| House          | ranch-style | wooden | gothic-revival | futuristic | townhouse | cape-cod | tower |
| Beverage   | almond-milk      | iced-tea   | sprite   | milk      | fanta       | lemonade       | juice     |

