The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia, bellflower, rose, amaryllis, iris, zinnia
 1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is the person watching action movies##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is the person who growsrose##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
11. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1
12. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action     | disaster  | sports       | musical       | animation  | satire   |
