.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
City: hannover, venice, nizza, paris, san-francisco, liverpool, boston
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, cabbage, grapes, cranberry, peach, strawberry, raspberry
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 3. the person traveling to boston is the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the person eating peach is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is the person traveling to nizza##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| City   | hannover  | boston | paris | san-francisco | liverpool     | venice | nizza |
| Food     | strawberry | cranberry      | raspberry | grapes    | peach | cabbage   | watermelon  |

