 4. the person eating onion is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

